Name: wmo_wis2_gc_downloaded_total
Description: Number of data items downloaded to Global Cache

Name: wmo_wis2_gc_downloaded_errors_total
Description: Number of download errors for Global Cache data

Name: wmo_wis2_gc_dataserver_status_flag
Description: Status of WIS2 Node dataserver (1-up and 0-down)

Name: wmo_wis2_gc_no_cache_total
Description: Number of data objects that Global Cache has been requested not to cache (based on the properties.cache flag)

Name: wmo_wis2_gc_cache_override_total
Description: Number of messages for which the Global Cache overrides the cache flag

Name: wmo_wis2_gc_integrity_failed_total
Description: Number of messages for which the integrity check failed
